Package: unicefData
Title: Download Indicators from UNICEF Data Warehouse
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R: person("Joao Pedro", "Azevedo", email = "jpazevedo@unicef.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A trilingual R, Python, and Stata client to fetch SDMX CSV series
    from UNICEF's Data Warehouse. Features include automatic pagination, caching
    with memoisation, country name lookups, metadata versioning (vintages),
    and comprehensive indicator support for SDG monitoring.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
